    "enContent": "<p>The API of the international website open platform is based on the HTTP protocol to call, and the developer (ISV) can directly use the official SDK provided by the international website open platform (which supports multiple languages, including request encapsulation, signature encryption, response interpretation, performance optimization, etc.) to call, or can encapsulate HTTP requests according to the AE protocol to call. </p><p><br></p><h5><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Invoke the process </strong></h5><p>According to the agreement of the international station:</p><p>1. Fill in the parameters </p><p>2. Generate a signature</p><p>3. Assemble HTTP requests</p><p>4. Initiate an HTTP request</p><p>5. Get an HTTP response</p><p>6. Interpret JSON/XML results</p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">API</strong><strong style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </strong><strong style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">call</strong><strong style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </strong><strong style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">entry </strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">API</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">format</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(61, 65, 69);\">: </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?method={api_path}&amp;{query}</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">APIs</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">registered</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">on</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">the</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">new</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">open</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">platform</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">: </span><a href=\"https://open.alibaba.com/doc/api.htm\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\">https://open.alibaba.com/doc/api.htm</a></li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">&nbsp;Instructions : </strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">1.</span>For details about which API should be called, see the protocol description of the Java sample code on the API documentation page of the API that is called: Specify the Protocal.TOP</p><p>2.{api_path} is the specific API path, and {query} is the parameter. </p><p>3.<span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Call</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Case: </span><a href=\"https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?app_key=34248607&amp;method=alibaba.icbu.product.list&amp;session=50000001219qGV4AgvCHpcSrEBGFRCp18441f79uzEkdQjVhSVEgajRqgt7b9bK&amp;sign_method=SHA256&amp;format=json&amp;sign=D5C578D3D9573F61FB04935F7B0E8AEB&amp;language=ENGLISH&amp;page_size=10&amp;timestamp=1726279603888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Click</a><a href=\"https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?app_key=34248607&amp;method=alibaba.icbu.product.list&amp;session=50000001219qGV4AgvCHpcSrEBGFRCp18441f79uzEkdQjVhSVEgajRqgt7b9bK&amp;sign_method=SHA256&amp;format=json&amp;sign=D5C578D3D9573F61FB04935F7B0E8AEB&amp;language=ENGLISH&amp;page_size=10&amp;timestamp=1726279603888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><a href=\"https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?app_key=34248607&amp;method=alibaba.icbu.product.list&amp;session=50000001219qGV4AgvCHpcSrEBGFRCp18441f79uzEkdQjVhSVEgajRqgt7b9bK&amp;sign_method=SHA256&amp;format=json&amp;sign=D5C578D3D9573F61FB04935F7B0E8AEB&amp;language=ENGLISH&amp;page_size=10&amp;timestamp=1726279603888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">here</a><a href=\"https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?app_key=34248607&amp;method=alibaba.icbu.product.list&amp;session=50000001219qGV4AgvCHpcSrEBGFRCp18441f79uzEkdQjVhSVEgajRqgt7b9bK&amp;sign_method=SHA256&amp;format=json&amp;sign=D5C578D3D9573F61FB04935F7B0E8AEB&amp;language=ENGLISH&amp;page_size=10&amp;timestamp=1726279603888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> to </a><a href=\"https://open-api.alibaba.com/sync?app_key=34248607&amp;method=alibaba.icbu.product.list&amp;session=50000001219qGV4AgvCHpcSrEBGFRCp18441f79uzEkdQjVhSVEgajRqgt7b9bK&amp;sign_method=SHA256&amp;format=json&amp;sign=D5C578D3D9573F61FB04935F7B0E8AEB&amp;language=ENGLISH&amp;page_size=10&amp;timestamp=1726279603888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">view </a></p><p><br></p>",
